query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char, MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress, MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation FROM aka_name AS an, complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, company_name AS cn, info_type AS it, info_type AS it3, keyword AS k, movie_companies AS mc, movie_info AS mi, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, person_info AS pi, role_type AS rt, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND cn.id = mc.company_id AND it.id = mi.info_type_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND rt.id = ci.role_id AND n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = pi.person_id AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND (chn.name like '%Maximus Decimus Meridius%' OR chn.name like '%Sherlock Holmes%' OR chn.name like '%Gandalf%') AND (pi.note like '%Merchant Phil%' OR pi.note like '%Jade SinClair PR%') AND (n.name like '%n%' OR n.name like '%x%' OR n.name like '%p%') AND (an.name like '%h%' OR an.name like '%W%') AND cn.country_code in ('sl','rw','br','id','yucs') AND (cn.name like '%A24%' OR cn.name like '%Amblin Partners%' OR cn.name like '%Pixar Animation Studios%') AND it3.info in ('alternate versions','trade mark','agent address','pictorial','runtimes','height','mpaa','magazine cover photo','article','LD year','LD quality program','quotes','goofs','LD catalog number','LD audio noise','LD contrast') AND t.title not like '%guitar%' AND t.title not like '%doll%' AND t.title not like '%city%' AND t.title not like '%knife%' AND t.title not like '%heart%' AND (k.keyword like '%magical%')
